Vigor of Activity(Corral of Balls): Interval 1 Epoch 1
Notes:
0 = Extremely low vigor: Sitting or standing still; minimal movement; looking at the balls without touching any; 1 = Low vigor: Some movement; plays with one or two balls in the immediate area; 2 = Moderate vigor: Moving to a couple of balls; walking around the corral; manipulating several balls; 3 = High vigor: Increased movements; walking from ball to ball; tossing several balls out of the corral; kicking a few balls; jumping or bouncing around; moving back and forth across the corral; manipulating several balls for short periods of time; 4 = Extremely high vigor: Rapid movements; running and jumping; throwing
balls in a rough manner; climbing out of corral.
